        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>, <date when="1825-02-15">15th Feb: 1825</date></p>
<p>Sir</p>

<p>Entertaining for your character the highest respect, I take the
liberty, although I have not the pleasure of a personal acquaintance
with you, to introduce to your acquaintance <persName>Mr. Ira Ingram</persName> who will
present this letter. <persName>Mr. Ingram</persName> is a gentleman of respectability, and
in every respect worthy your esteem and confidence. Any service it
may be in your power to render him will be thankfully remembered.</p>

<p><persName>H. Johnson,
Governor of the State of <placeName>Louisiana</placeName>.</persName></p>
<p><persName>Col. S. F. Austin</persName>.</p>


        </div1>
